desc: This book constitutes the refereed conference proceedings of the 31st British International Conference on Databases, BICOD 2017 – formerly known as BNCOD (British National Conference on Databases) – held in London, UK, in July 2017.

details.authors: Andrea Calì, Peter Wood, Nigel Martin, Alexandra Poulovassilis

title: Data Analytics: 31st British International Conference on Databases, BICOD 2017, London, UK, July 10-12, 2017, Proceedings (Lecture Notes in Computer Science)
